casebody.data:
James Anderson PLOTNER v. Louise Strother SIMS. No. 1715. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Oct. 10, 1938. Tom W. Campbell, of Little Rock, Ark., for appellant. V. E. Mclnnis, of Oklahoma City, Old., for appellee.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed with prejudice, on motion of appellant at appellant’s costs.
